                  </hi>. I live at 43, All Saints Road, Westbourne Park, and stand with a weighing machine at Moorgate Street Station—on this Friday evening, about 8 o'clock, I saw the prisoner there—I saw him throw away a purse.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
